This is a simplified version of the computer-database example from play 2.0 distribution. 

There are several branches in this repo:
 - original: this is the original example from play-2.0 distribution
 - simple-anorm: simplified. remove pagination, tests and sorting
 - simple-mongo: the finished ported application

The goal of this repo is to be used in a hands-on demonstration on how to port a anorm based play application to a mongodb one.
